Description: Professional download manager for VAXP-OS
 Vdownloader is a next-generation download manager with multi-threaded
 HTTP/HTTPS/FTP downloads and full BitTorrent support via libtorrent.
 Features include a stunning Glassmorphism UI, real-time speed graphs,
 clipboard monitoring, and browser extension integration.
 .
 Part of the VAXP-OS application ecosystem.
